Name: WireData
Description: Network data collected by the WireData solution using by the Dependency agent and Log analytics agent.

Properties.Name: Computer
Properties.Description: Computer name where data was collected

Properties.Name: SessionStartTime
Properties.Description: Start time of session

Properties.Name: SessionEndTime
Properties.Description: End time of session

Properties.Name: LocalIP
Properties.Description: IP address of the local computer

Properties.Name: LocalSubnet
Properties.Description: Subnet where data was collected

Properties.Name: LocalMAC
Properties.Description: Hold over field from old schema - attribute not collected

Properties.Name: LocalPortNumber
Properties.Description: Local port number

Properties.Name: RemoteIP
Properties.Description: Remote IP address used by the remote computer

Properties.Name: RemoteMAC
Properties.Description: Hold over field from old schema - attribute not collected

Properties.Name: RemotePortNumber
Properties.Description: Port number used by the remote IP address

Properties.Name: SessionID
Properties.Description: A unique value that identifies communication session between two IP addresses

Properties.Name: SequenceNumber
Properties.Description: Hold over field from old schema - attribute not collected

Properties.Name: SessionState
Properties.Description: Connected or disconnected

Properties.Name: SentBytes
Properties.Description: Number of bytes sent

Properties.Name: ReceivedBytes
Properties.Description: Amount of bytes received

Properties.Name: TotalBytes
Properties.Description: Total number of bytes sent during session

Properties.Name: ProtocolName
Properties.Description: Name of the network protocol used

Properties.Name: IPVersion
Properties.Description: IP version

Properties.Name: SentPackets
Properties.Description: Hold over field from old schema - attribute not collected

Properties.Name: ReceivedPackets
Properties.Description: Hold over field from old schema - attribute not collected

Properties.Name: Direction
Properties.Description: Inbound or outbound

Properties.Name: ApplicationProtocol
Properties.Description: Type of network protocol used

Properties.Name: ProcessID
Properties.Description: Windows process ID

Properties.Name: ProcessName
Properties.Description: Path and file name of the process

Properties.Name: ApplicationServiceName
Properties.Description: Hold over field from old schema - attribute not collected

Properties.Name: LatencyMilliseconds
Properties.Description: Hold over field from old schema - attribute not collected

Properties.Name: LatencySamplingTimeStamp
Properties.Description: Hold over field from old schema - attribute not collected

Properties.Name: LatencySamplingFailureRate
Properties.Description: Hold over field from old schema - attribute not collected

Properties.Name: MaliciousIP
Properties.Description: IP address of a known malicious source

Properties.Name: IndicatorThreatType
Properties.Description: Threat indicator detected is one of the following values Botnet C2 CryptoMining Darknet DDos MaliciousUrl Malware Phishing Proxy PUA Watchlist.

Properties.Name: Description
Properties.Description: Description of the observed threat.

Properties.Name: TLPLevel
Properties.Description: Traffic Light Protocol (TLP) Level is one of the defined values White Green Amber Red.

Properties.Name: Confidence
Properties.Description: Confidence level for Malicious IP identification. Values are 0 - 100.

Properties.Name: Severity
Properties.Description: Suspected malware severity

Properties.Name: FirstReportedDateTime
Properties.Description: The first time the provider reported the threat.

Properties.Name: LastReportedDateTime
Properties.Description: The last time the indicator was seen by Interflow.

Properties.Name: IsActive
Properties.Description: Indicates indicators are deactivated with True or False value.

Properties.Name: ReportReferenceLink
Properties.Description: Links to reports related to a given observable malicious IP threat.

Properties.Name: AdditionalInformation
Properties.Description: attribute not collected

Properties.Name: RemoteIPLongitude
Properties.Description: IP longitude value

Properties.Name: RemoteIPLatitude
Properties.Description: IP latitude value

Properties.Name: RemoteIPCountry
Properties.Description: Country/region of the remote IP address

Properties.Name: SourceSystem
Properties.Description: OpsManager

Properties.Name: MG
Properties.Description: Id of the management group for System Center Operations Manager agents.

Properties.Name: ManagementGroupName
Properties.Description: Name of the Operations Manager management group

Properties.Name: TenantId
Properties.Description: ID of the worksapce that stores this record

Properties.Name: TimeGenerated
Properties.Description: Time of the record
